longBusinessSummary: Styleclick, Inc. provides electronic commerce (e-commerce) technologies and services enabling its customers to sell their products online. The company offers such business clients a range of services and products, including Website design and development; product imaging and presentation; merchandising; and online sales, visualization, and merchandising technologies. Styleclick designs, builds, operates and hosts destination stores on the Web, assisting companies to increase sales, grow their customer base, and extend their brands via the Internet. Its e-commerce solutions incorporate software that enables high-volume transactional processing and a uniformly branded and consistently excellent customer experience. Styleclick integrates its online storefront application and merchandising and inventory management technology with reporting systems and back-end fulfillment and customer care to create commerce-driven offerings to help clients expand sales to customers across the Web. The company's technology platform leverages a central CRM-driven database for consumer profiling and direct marketing capabilities. Styleclick receives substantially all of its business from USA Electronic Commerce Solutions LLC (ECS), another USA Interactive company, to which the company provides e-commerce-enabling technology for certain third-party clients of ECS. The company was founded in 1988 and is based in Chicago, Illinois. Styleclick, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of IAC/InterActiveCorp.
